OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781750865
OL,3,CHealth worker cautioned over misuse of
OL,4,CKate's medical records for financial
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FA former healthcare worker at the
OL,8,FLondon Clinic has been cautioned by
OL,9,Fthe Information Commissioner's Office
OL,10,Fover the deliberate misuse of the
OL,11,FPrincess of Wales's private medical
OL,12,Frecords and offering to disclose them
OL,13,Ffor financial gain.
OL,15,FThe ICO began a criminal investigation
OL,16,Fin March 2024 into the unlawful
OL,17,Fobtaining and disclosure of medical
OL,18,Finformation to a third party without
OL,19,Fthe consent of the data controller,
OL,20,Fafter the London Clinic reported a
OL,21,Fbreach.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
