FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781750865
OL,3,CHealth worker cautioned over misuse of
OL,4,CKate's medical records for financial
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FAt the time, it was reported that at
OL,8,Fleast one member of staff had tried to
OL,9,Faccess Kate's notes while she was a
OL,10,Fpatient at the private hospital in
OL,11,FJanuary of that year.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FIn March 2024, ITV News was told that
OL,19,Fthree members of staff at the clinic
OL,20,Fwere being investigated for allegedly
OL,21,Ftrying to access royal medical records.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
