FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781750865
OL,3,CHealth worker cautioned over misuse of
OL,4,CKate's medical records for financial
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FThey faced disciplinary action
OL,8,Ffollowing a potential breach of data
OL,9,Fat The London Clinic, which treated
OL,10,Fboth the Princess of Wales and King
OL,11,FCharles in January 2024.
OL,13,FThe princess was told about the
OL,14,Fpotential data breach, as patients are
OL,15,Falways informed if there are any
OL,16,Fsuspicions that their private medical
OL,17,Frecords have been shared or accessed
OL,18,Fin an unauthorised manner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781750865
OL,3,CHealth worker cautioned over misuse of
OL,4,CKate's medical records for financial
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FThe hospital said at the time that any
OL,8,Fof its staff who had attempted to
OL,9,Faccess patient information would face
OL,10,F"disciplinary steps".
OL,12,FThe ICO said on Wednesday: "Following
OL,13,Fa full assessment under the Code for
OL,14,FCrown Prosecutors and the ICO's
OL,15,FProsecution Policy, the ICO issued a
OL,16,Fnow former healthcare professional
OL,17,Ffrom London with a formal caution in
OL,18,Frelation to an offence under section
OL,19,F170(5) of the Data Protection Act 2018.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@TO]tD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
