OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781750865
OL,3,CHealth worker cautioned over misuse of
OL,4,CKate's medical records for financial
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,F"The conduct involved the deliberate
OL,8,Fmisuse of highly sensitive personal
OL,9,Finformation and an offer to disclose
OL,10,Fit for financial gain, representing a
OL,11,Fclear breach of trust."
OL,13,FThe ICO said a caution was "the
OL,14,Fappropriate and proportionate
OL,15,Fenforcement response".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@WO]uD@\OUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
