PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781750865
OL,3,CHealth worker cautioned over misuse of
OL,4,CKate's medical records for financial
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FIt added: "We also considered whether
OL,8,Fthere were any wider organisational
OL,9,Fissues arising from the healthcare
OL,10,Fprovision in this matter. Based on the
OL,11,Fevidence available, we did not
OL,12,Fidentify any failings that would meet
OL,13,Fthe threshold for regulatory
OL,14,Fenforcement."
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
