FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781750865
OL,3,CHealth worker cautioned over misuse of
OL,4,CKate's medical records for financial
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FIan Hulme, executive director for
OL,8,Fregulatory supervision, said: "People
OL,9,Fshould be able to trust that the
OL,10,Fpersonal information they're giving to
OL,11,Fhealthcare settings is safe and
OL,12,Fprotected from exploitation. When this
OL,13,Ftrust is broken, it's right that the
OL,14,Flaw allows us to take action.
OL,16,F"We will not hesitate to pursue
OL,17,Fcriminal prosecution where it is
OL,18,Fnecessary and proportionate to do so."
OL,26,@pD@_OUxD@AOUzD@fO]
