PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781750865
OL,3,CHealth worker cautioned over misuse of
OL,4,CKate's medical records for financial
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FA London Clinic spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fall take considerable pride in
OL,9,Fdelivering the very highest standards
OL,10,Fof care and discretion for every
OL,11,Fpatient at The London Clinic. We are
OL,12,Fpleased our work with the ICO has
OL,13,Fbrought this sad and isolated incident
OL,14,Fto a conclusion. There were no
OL,15,Fregulatory breaches by the hospital."
OL,17,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,18,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,19,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,20,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson
